    airquality Dataset

    mtcars.Rd

    A dataframe that is derived from information collected about the daily air quality measurements in New York, May to September 1973.

    A dataframe that is derived from the 1974 Motor Trend US magazine, and comprises fuel consumption and 10 aspects of automobile design and performance for 32 automobiles (1973–74 models)

    mtcars

mtcars

    Format

    A data frame with 153 rows and 6 columns:

    Ozone

    numeric. Mean ozone in parts per billion from 1300 to 1500 hours at Roosevelt Island.

    Solar.R

    numeric. Solar radiation in Langleys in the frequency band 4000–7700 Angstroms from 0800 to 1200 hours at Central Park.

    Wind

    numeric. Average wind speed in miles per hour at 0700 and 1000 hours at LaGuardia Airport.

    Temp

    numeric. Charles River dummy variable (= 1 if tract bounds river; 0 otherwise).

    Month

    numeric. Month(1-12).

    Day

    numeric. Day of month (1--31).

    A data frame with 153 rows and 6 columns:

    mpg

    numeric. Miles/(US) gallon.

    cyl

    numeric. Number of cylinders.

    disp

    numeric. Displacement (cu.in.).

    hp

    numeric. Gross horsepower.

    drat

    numeric. Rear axle ratio.

    wt

    numeric. Weight (1000 lbs).

    qsec

    numeric. 1/4 mile time.

    vs

    numeric. Engine (0 = V-shaped, 1 = straight)

    am

    numeric. Transmission (0 = automatic, 1 = manual)

    gear

    numeric. Number of forward gears

    Source

    base R
